{"tid":1559041,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"支持休班警帶警棍出街","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:37:30.000Z","uid":179004,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd2757e7da178b274df2be8459022128d83acb35","tid":1559041,"uid":179004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"支持休班警帶警棍出街嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母</span></span><br />\n對唔住做咗標題黨，但係我有要事相求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hjMPY9Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhjMPY9Q.jpg&h=56fbdad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔離post (<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558360</a>)巴打都已經分析過<br />\n警察呢個做法係想合理化休班警扮示威者捉遊行人士，<br />\n到時遲啲打完人佢地記者會，<br />\n實會解釋啲休班警都係咁啱著黑色衫，<br />\n係執行緊公務。<br />\n<br />\n所以黎緊請<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣組</span>進場，<br />\n大大力用中英文，以及多國語言，<br />\n宣傳同譴責警方呢個即日生效嘅政策。<br />\n鑑於現時文宣速度同力度減低，<br />\n我地每位手足都有<span style=\"font-size: large;\">責任</span>係除咗係自己社交圈子嘅(如igfb)轉發同譴責外，亦要:<br />\n<br />\n1.多係地區fb group宣傳<br />\n例如 xxx之友，家在xxx上解釋呢件事<br />\n2. 向自己長輩親戚解釋<br />\n3. 自己print/自己畫banner去返屋企附近連儂牆貼<br />\n4. 周圍r生活上遇到嘅人講，例如看更，餐廳啲熟待應<br />\n5. 自己down reddit/Twitter/youtube向外宣傳<br />\n6. 集合自己學校/地區群組派傳單/街站<br />\n<br />\n因為呢件事係非常之不合理，<br />\n我地絕對唔可以比呢件事習慣，<br />\n一定要煲大呢件事，<br />\n用群眾壓力令警方收回，<br />\n佢地一意孤行就，<br />\n再用呢件事集合所有人為下一次民陣大遊行造勢。<br />\n<br />\n最後為大家附上:<br />\n記住我地背付緊<br />\n十位已去世的義士，<br />\n過千位被捕的手足，<br />\n數十位流亡海外的兄弟，<br />\n無數在運動中而受傷/殘障的家人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NYDCozW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNYDCozW.jpg&h=37ce3438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wXZJ3Co.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwXZJ3Co.jpg&h=062e0ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們只許勝，不許敗。<br />\n願榮光歸香港。"},{"pid":"b2e9e633669c9f7f112db39b957e824213a06586","tid":1559041,"uid":179004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:05:45.000Z","msg":"柒咗 post多次條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558360</a>"},{"pid":"3457531f8ed1fe431ef297356d8b09ce1111e223","tid":1559041,"uid":179004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"pushy"},{"pid":"a943fc1cfe99f90b74bf90e3246c2a275efb47a4","tid":1559041,"uid":179004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:06:22.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"adc49dc67a150c581cbfc97e15b7ce9baa8d30e8","tid":1559041,"uid":179004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:06:32.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"4c83633ea7647e1ff46b45e0bc31cab8be17ca0a","tid":1559041,"uid":179004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:07:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要文宣呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"15f21b4185e21c32f54890335d4d18a658dfb31c","tid":1559041,"uid":179004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/niUmQj4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FniUmQj4.jpg&h=3a1af32f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0005873da93d2ffe3bbc9fd38adf108c52dc17f","tid":1559041,"uid":179004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i3WPZdv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi3WPZdv.jpg&h=385d75c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fe7f5f7d4bf7d81b6515b7c32d445cabb75080b","tid":1559041,"uid":179004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9PVake.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%